  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Describe the resonant frequencies in instruments that can be modeled as a tube with symmetrical boundary conditions</item>
<item>Describe the resonant frequencies in instruments that can be modeled as a tube with anti-symmetrical boundary conditions</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
